transcript_chunks.text: so Nick where are we right now Tim I believe we're in the beautiful city of San Francisco exactly my hometown we went around the city with Pivot TV and showed them all of our favorite spots and found a couple of cool ways we can support local community projects yeah we had a crazy little adventure that you can watch over at takepart.com it's your town to see what makes San Francisco Our Town yeah we're all passionate about something so help us take that passion and turn it into an opportunity to get involved in your area remember it's your town get involved and check out our video at takepart.com it's your town
